## Key Finding

Our initial grammar was WRONG. We said DO/NEED/DONE. The data says:
- **Execution:** DO/DATA/DONE
- **Planning:** CHAIN/CLAIM/ORDER
- **Discovery:** REGISTRY/TERRAIN/VERIFY

These are three separate atom sets, not one. The grammar bifurcates under empirical pressure.

